                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Chargé d’Affaires</gloss> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Theeapia</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-09-30">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 30, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Peace between Turkey and Bulgaria was signed here yesterday evening.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Philip</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
